 commercial code troubled loan workouts creditors’ rights and bankruptcy he regularly serves as a member of the panel of bankruptcy trustees for the eastern district of virginia legal experience leclairryan richmond virginia   present  hazel  thomas richmond virginia     mcguire woods battle  boothe richmond virginia     law clerk honorable blackwell n shelley  memberships and affiliations member panel of bankruptcy trustees eastern district of virginia founding director business turnaround and finance association pastchairman richmond bar association bankruptcy section board memberships president virginia state golf association    distinctions listed in chambers usa americas leading business lawyers for bankruptcyrestructuring  listed among the best lawyers in america® for bankruptcy and creditordebtor rightsinsolvency and reorganization law and litigation  bankruptcy – listed in virginia business magazines legal elite for bankruptcycreditors’ rights – recognized by law  politics magazine as a virginia super lawyer in bankruptcy business – named top  virginia super lawyers by law  politics magazine  named top  richmond super lawyers by law  politics magazine  related content biography headlines related industries banking related practices bankruptcy  creditors rights business succession civil false claims act investigations  litigation recreational space education jd college of william  mary marshallwythe school of law  ba college of william  mary  bar admissions admitted only in virginia  client bill pay disclaimer and terms of usesite map advertising circular    leclairryan all rights reserved  attorney advertising case results depend upon a variety of factors unique to each case case results do not guarantee or predict a similar result in any future case verification code xi before sending your email to us please note and understand the followingthis website provides general information about leclairryan its practice areas and professional staff it is not intend